reviews.text:
Happy to report that the quality of the pasta and friendliness of the staff have been consistently carried over to this new location.

The seating is a lot more spacious than their Wanchai location and this one is super close to the MTR. Great place to catch up with friends.

Given how overpriced the nearby restaurants are (for sub-par quality), we have a real winner here!

Looking forward to coming back for more freshly made, hand crafted goodness.

(If you find this review helpful, please click on that like button, thanks.)
Excellent pasta, freshly made on premises. Really excellent service, friendly and prompt. Kids are well provided for, and the food is delicious.
Went for the free pasta and stayed for the wonderful experience. Nice cheese and tiramisu. Definitely would recommend to try!

Decor is good.,
Music is TOO loud. Staff singing 'Happy Birthday' had to compete with the background Motown sound. I like 70s Motown sound but it is definitely not a choice for an Italian joint.
Bread is cold.
Food: tagliolini was lukewarm and not inviting; the signature dish Pici cacio e Pepe   is far too chewy though the taste is good.
The only good stuff is panna cotta and tiramisu. I gave them one more star for these.
Not as good as the original in Wanchai.. pasta was not very fresh and sauces were bland.

reviews.text: Bit better than D2 ONE. But kinda screaming for 'please come in and spend moolah' vibe.
An excellent place for movie. Spacious and comfortable seating.

Nice mall which are on 2 building. No branded stuff like every mall. Some call this mall for hipster. 50% of the area are use as restaurant. The rest is handicarf art and indi store. Really hope the mall management can maintain this type of theme for long term. Foot traffic is kinda weak.
Another fabulous mall for local designers and non-chain stores!
The cinema is nice and clean.  Good to enjoy movie there

reviews.text: 此商場攪好多活動適合大人及小朋友遊玩好地方🎉
公仔機呃人的😭
今次係第一次帶孖女去大樹先生玩，對於佢地實在是一個新的體驗～ 食物就很一般，而且偏貴，但其實重點并不時它，大家都把食物放在桌子上，但沒有人在用餐⋯ 超搞笑的！
門口有市集，2、3F也有很多藝術類、手作的小型雜貨店，很適合年輕人來這裡逛逛。
